{"tid":2195593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31灣仔暴動案 高級督察稱當日逾500人與警方「 不友善地對峙」","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:48:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"24c06dc0512135ca247dfe84a1498ff8b02332d6","tid":2195593,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"去年8.31港島嚴重警民衝突中，包括「陣地社工」成員陳虹秀等八人被控暴動等罪，案件今在區域法院續審。當日到場的小隊指揮官供稱，收到指示要掃蕩及驅散軒尼詩道的示威者。當他們到達時，逾500名示威者在路障後與警方「不友善地對峙」。他的小隊清理路障，清出一條車道，讓兩架「水炮車」通過。及後小隊行至分域街時向前衝，在修頓球場對出拘捕了兩女三男，但他不知詳情，亦沒有跟進被捕者的情況，包括他們有否受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/C6QK3B7SNRHJNIBPV44RF4UNZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FC6QK3B7SNRHJNIBPV44RF4UNZ4%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=a74bc0ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FC6QK3B7SNRHJNIBPV44RF4UNZ4%2F&h=70acc3bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/C6QK3B7SNRHJNIBPV44RF4UNZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"44eadf608d082b3563ade3adf23ba4cbb2a03586","tid":2195593,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"調轉？"},{"pid":"4ca67c6408ffcb4ff0098a2e43e1bef8a931f43c","tid":2195593,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為500萬人"},{"pid":"4d23ec7139eda49993076c0f8d716ff7cd42b8fa","tid":2195593,"uid":146285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"一隻手掌拍得響?"},{"pid":"b13581ec4829eeb8f624dd903cf738cbf84a142d","tid":2195593,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"原因問自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21e07abff0264c508a52c5d6140b6a6ae4839f4","tid":2195593,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re